data.description: Welcome to your cozy retreat in the heart of Hinesville! This charming home offers single-level living with all the comforts you desire. This 1,350 square foot home offers 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms and an open concept floor plan. Also an additional room that will provide versatility for guests,a home office, or a hobby room. The expansive backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and recreation. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your own!
